metadata.description:
JACK & JAMO - The DJ Duo behind Shellz Orb NFT projects audio design, Trey Songs NFT & David Bowie NFT on Melos. Look Up is the first J&J solo release and features lyrics inspired by the Shellz Orb Animated Series show bible written by The Neese Brothers, Executive producers of Umbrella Academy on Netflix. 

The duo met in Los Angeles in 2015 and have been performing live DJ sets with Electric Guitar + Synthesisers & producing music ever since. Under their monikers Jamieson Hill and JÃ…CK FORD, they released an official remix of Tainted Love by Soft Cell that charted on Spotify for some time. 

They have been booked by clients such as Calvin Klien, Stella Artois, Lucky Brand, Joe's Jeans and played the mainstage at Area 51 during Web3Expo in Las Vegas. 

This first Web 3 release will be the kick-off to many Web3 bangers and you should expect to see JACK & JAMO DJing all the hot upcoming NFT parties.
